org.apache.flink.streaming.api.datastream

类 SplitStream<OUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.datastream.DataStream<OUT>
      • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.datastream.SplitStream<OUT>
  • 类型参数:
    OUT - The type of the elements in the Stream

    @PublicEvolving
public class SplitStream<OUT>
extends DataStream<OUT>
    The SplitStream represents an operator that has been split using an OutputSelector. Named outputs can be selected using the select(java.lang.String...) function. To apply transformation on the whole output simply call the transformation on the SplitStream
